                    <path d="M3 7L12 11L21 7" />
                    <!-- Label/Stickers on the Box -->
                    <rect x="9" y="13" width="6" height="3" rx="0.5" ry="0.5" />
                </svg>

            </span>
            <h4>3. Keep Labels</h4>
            <p>
                If there are any labels or stickers on the box, please leave them on and we will remove them. If you attempt to remove the labels, damage caused to the box by improper removal of a label may disqualify the submission.
